le.io/talk/2025_06_02_cec_ansible_power_workshop</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://fale.io/talk/2025_06_02_cec_ansible_power_workshop</guid><description/></item><item><title>Upcoming Events: CEC, Flock, and DevConf.cz</title><link>https://fale.io/blog/2025/05/31/upcoming-events-cec-flock-and-devconf_cz</link><media:content type="image/webp" medium="image" width="728" height="350" url="https://fale.io/img/posts/2025_05_31_upcoming_events_cec_flock_and_devconf_cz.webp"/><pubDate>Sat, 31 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://fale.io/blog/2025/05/31/upcoming-events-cec-flock-and-devconf_cz</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;In the coming couple of weeks I&amp;rsquo;ll be heading to the Common Europe Congress (CEC2025), Flock 2025, and DevConf.cz 2025, some of the best community-driven events in the ecosystem.
