_19_fedora_coreos_on_hetzner_dedicated_server.webp"/><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://fale.io/blog/2023/10/19/fedora-coreos-on-hetzner-dedicated-server</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Over the last few years, I&amp;rsquo;ve moved many of my systems to Immutable versions of Fedora.
