Ansible Controller is the name of the Red Hat Ansible Automation Platform 2 component based on AWX.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>gopass in Fedora</title><link>https://fale.io/blog/2022/04/25/gopass-in-fedora</link><media:content type="image/webp" medium="image" width="728" height="350" url="https://fale.io/img/posts/2022_04_25_gopass_in_fedora.webp"/><pubDate>Mon, 25 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://fale.io/blog/2022/04/25/gopass-in-fedora</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;I started to use ZX2C4&amp;rsquo;s &lt;code&gt;pass&lt;/code&gt; back in 2016 to manage my passwords.
