The idea behind this small software is to create a more flexible way to keep the Google Cloud Disks Snapshots tidy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Google Cloud does provide a very nice way to &lt;a href="https://cloud.google.com/compute/docs/disks/scheduled-snapshots"&gt;automatically snapshot your disks&lt;/a&gt;, leveraging the &lt;strong&gt;resource policies&lt;/strong&gt;.
