The error was:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;ERROR! Syntax Error while loading YAML.
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;As soon as I saw the error, I already guessed which problems could trigger such error: it&amp;rsquo;s either a bad usage of spaces, a badly escaped column within a value, or a variable escaping problem.
